colname(close_ts) <- 'close'

Error in colname(close_ts) <- "close" : 
  could not find function "colname<-"

Look at the acf and pacf, the data seems to be AR(1). To look at the periodogram, we need to remove the trend first.

acf(close_ts)

pacf(close_ts)

spec.pgram(close_ts)
